{
  "stem": "6258.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then later on, I had that feeling that the whole world kept their breath-- their breath, suddenly.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And suddenly, I heard some strange noise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And now more and more and more-- and they were the bombers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was when the first bombs fell on Krakow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now-- well, and nobody knew exactly what was going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, this was '39, so I was about 13, almost 14.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, there was this enormous with people afterwards-- nobody knew what was going on, whether there is a real war.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then we heard from the radio that we are being invaded, and-- and what is going on?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that men should go to the east.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I looked my father went to, to-- well, for the mobilization place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then they said, every man should go, and we were being evacuated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "His bank was evacuated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were evacuated with-- with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is the reason our nanny stayed in home, and we left with Father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, nobody could find that place where they were supposed to get uniforms, and this and that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was incredible to go with the masses of people and soldiers, and everybody was frightened.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody knew what is going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were really leaving and going with the-- it was like, like, you know, surge of people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no way to go back-- everybody was afraid of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the east.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everywhere was, well, that Polish army was moving to the east and through Romania and Hungary, later onwards in France, to England.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and everybody was going, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There only Warsaw-- stay, stop the Germans for about six weeks, and was-- there was the fighting and the battle.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But here, there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
